## Model of subnet planning, design and implementation processes.
+-------------------+        +---------------------+       +-------------------------+
| -1 Analyze Needs  | --->   | -2 Design Subnets   | --->  | -3 Plan Implementation  |
+-------------------+        +---------------------+       +-------------------------+
|  - # Subnets      |        |  - Choose Network   |       |  - Subnets -> Locations |
|  - # Hosts/Subnet |        |  - Choose 1 Mask    |       |  - Static IP            |
|  - 1 Size Subnet  |        |  - List All Subnets |       |  - DHCP Ranges          |
+-------------------+        +---------------------+       +-------------------------+


